Metadata.Description: Detects anomalies in the input time series. Returns anomaly score and alert indicator

Analyze input time series and output data period (if data period == 1, means no significant seasonality detected). Also output seasonally adjusted time series if SeasonalAdjust is set to TRUE and significant seasonality has been detected
